{"tid":2257721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★HK No IT】2020年10月---代號「疾響」反罪惡行動，檢獲22,000隻色情光碟","createTime":"2020-10-25T12:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T12:31:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd476b69d4a90e5481dd512a00a276ad3d1411b","tid":2257721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:02:35.000Z","msg":"為針對犯罪集團及黑幫分子的罪行及打擊其收入來源，旺角警區於前日及昨日(23及24日)執行代號「疾響」反罪惡行動，動用超過200名軍裝及刑事部警員，突擊搜查區內17個地點，巡查超過60個持牌酒吧、夜總會、桑拿浴室、遊戲機中心、賓館等場所。<br />\n<br />\n行動中，警方檢獲10部釣魚機、<span class=\"xx-large\">約22,000隻色情光碟</span>、約34克懷疑「K仔」、約7克懷疑冰毒、約6克懷疑可卡因、約5克懷疑霹靂可卡因、一批酒精類飲品、約24,000港元現金等，證物總值超過70萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201025/bkn-20201025151957602-1025_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201025%2Fbkn-20201025151957602-1025_00822_001.html&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=1cc3fc9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201025/bkn-20201025151957602-1025_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8ad1048263d78853861fbc7c2cfa46ef8522dcb5","tid":2257721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8916a542d392ea2db87545dd9e591c395d584431","tid":2257721,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201025/photo/bkn-20201025151957602-1025_00822_001_01b.jpg?20201025171127\" data-thumbnail-